# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.0.1] - 2026-07-02

### Added

- Working game: standard mode with rectangular board, stopwatch, 3 pre-set difficulties and a custom difficulty.
- Linux build tools, with AppImage build tool, build pipeline bash script and logo asset.
- This changelog.
- A TODO file.

### Fixed

- Fix semantic versioning in pubspec.yaml.

